name: Battery Eliminator
description:
Battery eliminator for any bike with a magneto ignition. 
This device eliminates the need of a battery, it is maintenance free and weight about 50 grams. It suits most two stroke bikes e.g Tzr125-250, Rgv250, Nsr250, Rd350-500 and most single cylinder bikes. 

Hand fabricated by a two stroke junkie. 

"Free worldwide shipping"

name: Nsr250 & Crm250 PGM repair-service
description:
A repair-service for non or partially working PGM units. 

You will have to post the unit to me, I will repair it and then post it back to you.

For Crm250 units I only repair RC Valve problems. 
For Nsr250 units I repair all of the problems that might occur but please ask for a quote if your unit has multiple issues. 

Derestriction of PgmII & PgmIII units for Nsr250 bikes is available at no extra charge. Just ask for it.

"Free worldwide shipping back"

name: YPVS Programmable modification service
description:
Modification of your stock YPVS controller to a fully reprogrammable unit, for most Yamaha bikes. 

After the modification the timing cycle of the exhaust valves will be fully adjustable. A corresponding chart with suggested settings is included. 

This modification is available for many Yamaha motorcycles including Rd250/350/500, Tzr250 1KT/2MA, DT125/200, Tz250 up to '90 models etc. 


"Free worldwide shipping back"

name: Crm250 AR PGM repair-service
description:
A repair-service of PGM units for Crm250 AR bikes. 

This repair is for AR PGM units with Rc Valve problems -only-. 

"Free worldwide shipping back"

name: Adjustable Power Jet Kit
description: Universal power jet kit that can be externally adjustable. For use on all two stroke carburetors. Check the main site for installation procedure and info on tuning.
